data.description: ***$5,000 seller credit to buy down rate or closing cost*** Dive into the perfect blend of comfort and convenience with this fantastic 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath home! Step inside to discover a beautifully designed space featuring a mix of tile flooring for easy maintenance and plush carpeting in the bedrooms for added comfort. The kitchen has granite countertops and is freshly painted throughout the home to create a welcoming atmosphere. With 1,800 square feet of living space, this home offers room to grow and entertain. But that's not all – step outside, and you'll find a great-sized pool, perfect for making the most of those sunny days. Plus, you can enjoy peace of mind knowing that the roof is just 2 years old. Located just minutes away from the excitement of the Globe Life Field and AT&T Stadium, as well as major highways, this home is not only a comfortable haven but also an ideal hub for all your entertainment and commuting needs.
